BATTLE OF THE BARBIES BREAST CANCER AWARENESS FASHION SHOW 🎀

Weekend Recap: I attended Battle of The Barbie #breastcancerawareness #fashionshow over the weekend. 
The theme was Barbie. As much as I love color, Barbie just isn’t me, so I went dark. 🖤 Rockstar Barbie was born. 
Here’s a secret, this look is repurposed! You do not have to put away your “summer clothes” (I don’t believe in seasonal wear, clothes are what you make them) Just find new ways to wear them. 

Same with your summer shoes (my only rule is once the snow hits, open toe shoes are out!) Adding socks gives your open to shoe an extended life, and adds edge to your look! 

It’s getting cool in the Midwest, so threw on some textured leggings and a turtleneck under a 2 piece skirt and top. Fully dressed, and still turning heads 😜
